description: "Men and women dancing to the waltz of spring of countless flowers now still supports one another to protect this eternal love on this happy occasion! " To appreciate the adventurers who have been supporting us for a long time, the famous Kafra Company specially launched a special small card in the form of a monthly magazine. Hold it and you will feel its magical power. It's practical and highly collectible.
